<math>{\it Si} \left( z \right) =z{\frac {d}{dz}}w \left( z \right) +2\,{
\frac {d^{2}}{d{z}^{2}}}w \left( z \right) +z{\frac {d^{3}}{d{z}^{3}}}
w \left( z \right) =0</math>

即：

<math>w \left( z \right) ={\it \_C1}+{\it \_C2}\,{\it Si} \left( z \right) 
+{\it \_C3}\,{\it Ci} \left( z \right)</math>

